## Group Notifications

Notifications are messages sent by the system or triggered by other users which bring important information to the user.

## Notifications [/user/notifications{?token,unread,readall}]

+ Parameters
    + token (required, string, `eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6ImFkbWluIiwiaWF0IjoxNDMzMjQ0OTQ5LCJleHAiOjE0MzMzMzEzNDl9.WoICqJy2POSkt-NhwOjcdbI4hYMw4lR6g5HjiogzhHE`) ... This login token is generated by login. It is required for any action performed by an user.
    + unread (optional, boolean, `true`) ... used to bring only the unread notifications.
    + readall (optional, boolean, `false`) ... used to bring all notifications.

